{"tid":952640,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［爆旋雨遮］一人一個雨遮設計比賽","createTime":"2018-12-23T10:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T11:40:34.000Z","uid":204656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbc46ce1590ea55261345cc90175dcefb8e03a4","tid":952640,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"係人都知香港地擔遮真係唔洗拎牌，今日呢場雨都唔例外。一行多人少少嘅地方大家就我要與你硬碰以爆裂極高速旋動，插眼、洗頭有遮似無遮咁成身濕Q曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以係未有監管前為求自保應該裝備好自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人推薦防守型既雨遮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L322yy1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL322yy1.png&h=6ef38982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個透明度高 又夠闊 活動空間大 基本都唔會掂到上半身 又夠大可以頂走人地 夠曬霸道<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一款都推薦既就係呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gE1ZAOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgE1ZAOv.png&h=6e607c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蚊帳x雨傘 <br />\n優點係比上面透氣度高 連腳都可以可以防埋 亦比較輕巧 仲可以防埋蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就活動空間較小 組裝麻煩 同埋易污糟要洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇攻擊型嘅巴打講下自己既設計呢<br />\n識轉嘅話應該好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f5f9af67eb1b92250848778277ea1cdb601a23","tid":952640,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"國王的雨遮"},{"pid":"77c7c4da029022a30c5f607fc609cbaf25448a8e","tid":952640,"uid":163404,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEMSbqV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEMSbqV.png&h=bfa4c7ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3fe3c6f9d6b239597a1409e223ad081959301d","tid":952640,"uid":176063,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fd707cf2c169982fbc3ad66693901f20d91ffd1","tid":952640,"uid":96708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eTMb2UkW4xY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeTMb2UkW4xY&d=HLK%2BsP7WG11W0TcKxuSXqsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=26609a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eTMb2UkW4xY</a>"},{"pid":"99fedd44b5abae59ecee511583dddd800c7a6e67","tid":952640,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3fe3c6f9d6b239597a1409e223ad081959301d","tid":952640,"uid":176063,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"頂你 直頭棄防<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c20907c6d8f6b24bf34c365a0b6ded78f4dfde5","tid":952640,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"第一個摺咗之後係點？<br />\n呢個先係重點"},{"pid":"a0db51e25ec964fcd8f6ef641b7701e23aa3b319","tid":952640,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c20907c6d8f6b24bf34c365a0b6ded78f4dfde5","tid":952640,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"第一個摺咗之後係點？<br />\n呢個先係重點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"佢應該係三角型咁摺上去"},{"pid":"1474300df8121888f742dfb4cb126ba47d69427d","tid":952640,"uid":14452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p